<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-5138] HTTP component always use a CachedOutputStream</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-5138</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Even with streamCache set to false (which is the default situation), the HTTP (and HTTP4) component (in producer mode) always create a CachedOutputStream.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should use a CachedOutputStream only if streamCache is true to the context.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
